{"tid":797827,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「樓爆樓爆系列」走資再現 銀行結餘穿800億","createTime":"2018-08-28T22:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T01:46:43.000Z","uid":115719,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3a04534774efdb4bcaaa7da8548ad35f3b39ef","tid":797827,"uid":115719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:19:04.000Z","msg":"為防止市場出現恐慌情緒，陳德霖周四大派定心丸，指香港銀行體系有足夠的流動性應付資金大規模流動，該局亦隨時準備透過調較總額達1萬億港元的外匯基金票據發行量，應對資金可能出現急劇外流的情況。 <br />\n<br />\n外匯基金票據如同短期債券，銀行可視之為抵押品，向金管局取得流動資金。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">倘若市場資金緊絀，金管局亦可提早贖回票據，或者減少票據的發行量，屆時以票據形式鎖起的資金，將回流銀行體系結餘，增加市場流動性。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/061453_7d4ac776bf3ed1f0084260220698afab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F061453_7d4ac776bf3ed1f0084260220698afab.png&h=38aa8c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見成個財經台都係結餘新聞<br />\n其實做物鳩者？<br />\n睇少陣蘋果日報啦<br />\n個結餘金管局可以令佢升返嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋果800億係借唔到出街既錢<br />\n唔係全部銀行得返800億呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec3a6c8a7624674d7158b762f953ed377f29179","tid":797827,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:20:42.000Z","msg":"要爆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e017fb0c66bac170f1e9d034e19f9f2c3b68e57","tid":797827,"uid":115719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:22:18.000Z","msg":"2018年貨幣供應量係1998既差唔多8倍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7d68172e049488c023b18adba5ca7fd7e87063","tid":797827,"uid":51294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:32:23.000Z","msg":"好驚咁喎"},{"pid":"984ad4631aec3232e8419763ed758e03b38c29f1","tid":797827,"uid":35930,"